General.Name: Cliq Digital AG
General.Description: Cliq Digital AG sells subscription-based streaming services that bundle movies and series, music, audiobooks, sports, and games to consumers worldwide. It licenses streaming content from partners, bundles it, and sells the content through its various streaming services. The company is specializing in online advertising and creating streaming services that are advertised towards specific consumer groups. Cliq Digital AG is headquartered in Düsseldorf, Germany and has offices in Amsterdam, London, Paris, and Toronto.
